<h1>想</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#009900;">xiǎng</span><span class=alesi>(xiang3)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciation of 想 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 想</h2><div class=abo>
<p><b>Unihan definition:</b> <a href="/dictionary/think" style="color:black;">think</a>, <a href="/dictionary/speculate" style="color:black;">speculate</a>, <a href="/dictionary/plan" style="color:black;">plan</a>, consider</p><p><b>Number of strokes:</b> 13<br><small>Examples of other characters consisting of 13 strokes: <a href="/character/意" title="yi4: thought, idea, opinion; think">意</a>, <a href="/character/新" title="xin1: new, recent, fresh, modern">新</a>, <a href="/character/解" title="jie3: loosen, unfasten, untie; explain">解</a>, <a href="/character/数" title="shu4: number; several, count; fate">数</a>, <a href="/character/感" title="gan3: feel, perceive, emotion">感</a>, <a href="/character/像" title="xiang4: a picture, image, figure; to resemble">像</a>, <a href="/character/路" title="lu4: road, path, street; journey">路</a>, <a href="/character/满" title="man3: fill; full, satisfied">满</a>, <a href="/character/照" title="zhao4: shine, illumine, reflect">照</a>, <a href="/character/跟" title="gen1: heel; to follow, accompany; with">跟</a></small></p><p><b>Radical:</b> <a href="/character/心" title="Kangxi radical 61">心</a>&nbsp;61.9</p><p><b>HSK level:</b> 1 <br><small>Other HSK 1 characters: <a href="/character/开" title="kai1: open; initiate, begin, start">开</a>, <a href="/character/前" title="qian2: in front, forward; preceding">前</a>, <a href="/character/本" title="ben3: root, origin, source; basis">本</a>, <a href="/character/她" title="ta1: she, her">她</a>, <a href="/character/样" title="yang4: shape, form, pattern, style">样</a>, <a href="/character/机" title="ji1: desk; machine; moment">机</a>, <a href="/character/些" title="xie1: little, few; rather, somewhat">些</a>, <a href="/character/十" title="shi2: ten, tenth; complete; perfect">十</a>, <a href="/character/小" title="xiao3: small, tiny, insignificant">小</a>, <a href="/character/好" title="hao3: good, excellent, fine; well">好</a> <a href="/character-list/hsk/level-1" title="List of HSK 1 characters" style="white-space: 